01:59.920 --> 02:00.640
<i>My name is Xiong Dun.</i>

02:01.000 --> 02:01.880
<i>Xiong, like a bear.</i>

02:01.880 --> 02:02.840
<i>Dun, like Newton.</i>

02:03.160 --> 02:04.080
<i>Tomorrow,</i>

02:04.080 --> 02:05.400
<i>I'll be turning 29.</i>

02:06.080 --> 02:06.760
<i>Alexander Bell</i>

02:06.760 --> 02:08.240
<i>invented the telephone when he was 29.</i>

02:08.800 --> 02:09.759
<i>Murakami</i>

02:09.759 --> 02:11.520
<i>started writing novels when he was 29.</i>

02:12.880 --> 02:13.760
<i>Spielberg</i>

02:13.760 --> 02:15.520
<i>directed "Jaws" when he was 29.</i>

02:15.520 --> 02:18.400
<i>and at 29, Steve Jobs introduced the Macintosh.</i>

02:18.400 --> 02:19.600
<i>I believe,</i>

02:19.600 --> 02:22.200
<i>the next 29-year-old to influence the world,</i>

02:22.200 --> 02:23.880
<i>has to be me!</i>

02:57.480 --> 02:58.240
<i>If</i>

02:58.240 --> 03:00.280
<i>the butterfly effect does exist.</i>

03:00.280 --> 03:01.080
<i>Then I think,</i>

03:01.080 --> 03:02.400
<i>I must be the butterfly,</i>

03:02.400 --> 03:05.800
<i>that could flap its wings,
and change the world.</i>

03:29.400 --> 03:30.720
Hey you!

03:31.480 --> 03:32.480
Do you have a death wish?

03:32.480 --> 03:33.840
Hurry up!

03:38.360 --> 03:39.320
<i>Fine,</i>

03:39.320 --> 03:40.800
<i>you got me.</i>

03:41.200 --> 03:42.600
<i>In this city,</i>

03:42.600 --> 03:44.440
<i>I'm no butterfly.</i>

03:44.880 --> 03:47.760
<i>Maybe a moth at best.</i>

03:53.440 --> 03:54.280
<i>Perhaps,</i>

03:54.280 --> 03:55.600
<i>for most girls,</i>

03:55.600 --> 03:58.520
<i>success means having the perfect wedding.</i>

04:05.520 --> 04:06.680
<i>But,</i>

04:07.320 --> 04:08.400
<i>that's not me.</i>

04:08.400 --> 04:10.000
We gather here today,

04:10.360 --> 04:11.760
to join together this man

04:12.160 --> 04:14.400
and this woman, in holy matrimony.

04:15.000 --> 04:16.360
If anyone

04:16.680 --> 04:17.640
has any objections,

04:18.399 --> 04:21.120
please speak now, or forever hold your peace.

04:37.440 --> 04:39.200
Sorry.

04:44.320 --> 04:46.000
If no one objects,

04:46.560 --> 04:47.440
Okay.

04:47.440 --> 04:49.200
Excuse me. I had to work late last night.

04:49.200 --> 04:49.840
Mr. Jiang.

04:49.840 --> 04:50.880
I didn't miss anything,right?

04:50.880 --> 04:52.480
I already said you didn't have to come.

04:53.640 --> 04:55.880
This is way too important to miss.

04:57.920 --> 04:59.520
Through good times and bad,

04:59.520 --> 05:00.320
in sickness or health...

05:00.320 --> 05:01.720
<i>To be honest,</i>

05:01.720 --> 05:04.880
<i>if it wasn't for leaving a good impression
on the boyfriend's parents,</i>

05:04.880 --> 05:07.400
<i>I'd be home sleeping, right about now.</i>

05:11.720 --> 05:13.160
Look over here.

05:13.160 --> 05:14.640
Smile. OK.

05:14.640 --> 05:15.720
Cousin and cousin-in-law,

05:15.720 --> 05:16.760
I'm Xiong Dun.

05:17.600 --> 05:19.120
You are Chuan's girlfriend right?

05:19.120 --> 05:19.840
That's me!

05:19.840 --> 05:21.280
You are really pretty!

05:24.160 --> 05:25.600
You got a loose thread

05:28.560 --> 05:29.840
Sorry.

05:29.840 --> 05:31.320
I pulled too hard.

05:31.320 --> 05:32.840
It's a loose thread.

05:34.800 --> 05:36.240
It really is a loose thread.

05:41.240 --> 05:42.440
If you are tired,

05:42.440 --> 05:43.840
you can go home and sleep.

05:44.160 --> 05:45.440
No one would mind.

05:45.440 --> 05:46.560
No, I'm okay.

05:46.560 --> 05:48.040
Why would I be tired?

05:49.480 --> 05:50.880
I'm doing this for you.

05:50.880 --> 05:51.680
Right?

05:56.120 --> 05:57.680
That poop-haired lady,

05:57.680 --> 05:59.280
is that the groom's mom?

06:00.400 --> 06:01.640
That's my mom.

06:03.480 --> 06:04.440
I'm sorry.

06:09.840 --> 06:11.320
I should go say hello.

06:11.760 --> 06:12.720
That's okay.

06:13.240 --> 06:14.120
More eating.

06:15.080 --> 06:16.000
Less talking.

06:31.040 --> 06:33.040
Here, this is for you.

06:33.920 --> 06:35.040
It will guarantee

06:35.480 --> 06:36.920
a happy marriage in the near future.

06:38.480 --> 06:40.480
There are two types of bosses in the world,

06:40.480 --> 06:42.560
There are only two kinds of men in this world,

06:42.560 --> 06:44.280
dumb ones and dumber ones.

06:44.280 --> 06:45.720
cowards and cheaters.

06:46.040 --> 06:47.160
Which one would you choose?

06:47.680 --> 06:50.200
And a Virgo on top of all that,

06:50.200 --> 06:52.160
now that's one of a kind.

06:52.160 --> 06:53.280
That's what my boss is like.

06:53.280 --> 06:54.480
Right on her chin,

06:54.480 --> 06:56.160
there's a huge mole.

06:56.160 --> 06:59.320
She spends all day covering it up,
again and again, and again.

06:59.320 --> 07:01.560
The harder she tries, the more obvious it is.

07:01.560 --> 07:03.760
Stop trying to hide it.

07:03.760 --> 07:05.600
I mean what's the point?

07:06.160 --> 07:07.720
Where are my applause?

07:10.720 --> 07:13.400
I just love champagne.

07:14.120 --> 07:14.760
Damn it.

07:14.760 --> 07:16.240
She is so freaking heavy!

07:16.480 --> 07:17.160
<i>Lao Zheng</i>

07:17.440 --> 07:18.360
<i>is a woman.</i>

07:18.600 --> 07:20.120
<i>She's a small business owner,</i>

07:20.120 --> 07:22.000
<i>and amateur boxing enthusiast.</i>

07:22.000 --> 07:23.800
<i>Her punches are
steady, accurate, and fierce.</i>

07:23.800 --> 07:25.720
<i>And as a person, not one bit less.</i>

07:34.880 --> 07:35.840
<i>Your typical Beijing chic.</i>

07:37.400 --> 07:38.440
<i>When she's around girls,</i>

07:38.440 --> 07:39.520
<i>she's manly.</i>

07:39.520 --> 07:40.680
<i>And when she's around guys...</i>

07:40.680 --> 07:41.880
<i>even manlier.</i>

07:42.360 --> 07:43.400
<i>She loves plaid shirts,</i>

07:43.400 --> 07:44.720
<i>dislikes pretty dresses.</i>

07:45.120 --> 07:46.520
<i>Wherever she goes,</i>

07:46.520 --> 07:48.400
<i>a trail of screams follow.</i>

07:50.000 --> 07:50.840
Let me go.

07:50.840 --> 07:52.320
I can walk by myself.

07:52.320 --> 07:54.360
Stop messing around.

07:54.680 --> 07:55.520
<i>Emmy.</i>

07:55.520 --> 07:57.560
<i>My BFF and roommate.</i>

07:57.560 --> 08:00.520
<i>Born smack in the middle of
the Yantze river delta area.</i>

08:00.920 --> 08:01.760
<i>She likes astrology...</i>

08:01.760 --> 08:02.760
<i>loves Tarot cards!</i>

08:05.120 --> 08:06.000
<i>Likes Koreans dramas...</i>

08:06.000 --> 08:07.200
<i>loves American shows!</i>

08:11.760 --> 08:12.920
<i>She loves selfies...</i>

08:14.480 --> 08:15.680
<i>but no peace signs, please.</i>

08:16.160 --> 08:17.360
<i>Loves working...</i>

08:17.360 --> 08:18.400
<i>hates overtime.</i>

08:19.040 --> 08:20.560
<i>Even though she always has to...</i>

08:22.320 --> 08:24.160
You got it now?

08:25.800 --> 08:26.920
<i>She is an actuary working for
a Japanese company,</i>

08:27.280 --> 08:29.600
<i>with an insanely unreasonable boss.</i>

08:29.600 --> 08:31.600
<i>That's why she's always exhausted.</i>

08:34.480 --> 08:35.760
Push! Just a little more! Push!

08:37.000 --> 08:37.880
<i>Well, okay.</i>

08:37.880 --> 08:39.600
<i>I made up that last part.</i>

08:39.600 --> 08:41.600
<i>But it really, really is that bad.</i>

08:43.280 --> 08:44.480
Holy crap!

08:44.480 --> 08:45.720
Damn that's exhausting.

08:46.600 --> 08:49.000
You always mess with me
at the most important parts.

08:50.640 --> 08:51.720
Play.

08:59.440 --> 09:00.240
That's my man!

09:00.240 --> 09:01.080
Move.

09:02.400 --> 09:04.160
I'm here to protect you.

09:04.480 --> 09:05.440
Step back.

09:05.760 --> 09:07.600
Me and my love are going zombie killing!

09:07.840 --> 09:08.600
Demons,

09:08.600 --> 09:09.480
back away!

09:12.320 --> 09:12.880
Emmy,

09:12.880 --> 09:14.040
I'm really sorry.

09:14.040 --> 09:15.160
Gotta go.

09:15.160 --> 09:15.760
Lao Zheng.

09:20.200 --> 09:21.120
There are people inside.

09:21.120 --> 09:22.480
Let's hide for a while.

09:22.480 --> 09:24.040
I would rather be killed.

09:27.320 --> 09:29.120
It's not safe outside.

09:50.200 --> 09:51.120
Oh my god.

09:51.120 --> 09:52.480
When did you come in?

09:53.080 --> 09:55.800
Xiao Xia asked you if
you remember what day today is?

09:57.320 --> 09:58.280
Deadline date!

09:59.000 --> 10:00.880
How many did I tell you to finish last time?

10:01.440 --> 10:02.880
Procrastination!

10:05.760 --> 10:07.480
There's something wrong with you right?

10:08.880 --> 10:09.840
Nothing's wrong with me.

10:12.680 --> 10:14.240
What's the matter with you?

10:15.160 --> 10:16.080
Nothing.

10:16.320 --> 10:17.320
What are you saying?

10:17.320 --> 10:19.000
Are you out of your mind?

10:19.240 --> 10:21.200
That wasn't a question.

10:24.400 --> 10:26.280
Last time you said to finish five,

10:26.520 --> 10:27.640
so I put in more hours and finished it.

10:27.640 --> 10:28.600
It's all done.

10:28.600 --> 10:31.040
More hours? Doing what, goofing around?

10:31.040 --> 10:32.560
Last time I said seven!

10:32.560 --> 10:33.800
You said five!

10:33.800 --> 10:34.600
I'm sure of it.

10:34.600 --> 10:35.320
If you'd said seven,

10:35.320 --> 10:36.560
there's no way I would finish that,

10:36.560 --> 10:37.920
so I wouldn't have agreed in the first place.

10:37.920 --> 10:39.600
Are you saying that it was my mistake?

10:39.600 --> 10:40.560
Are you?

10:40.560 --> 10:41.440
Sounds to me like you
don't want your job anymore,

10:41.440 --> 10:42.840
If that's the case, you can get out.

10:42.840 --> 10:44.280
There are a lot of people waiting for your spot.

10:45.040 --> 10:47.120
What, you think I wanna be...

10:47.120 --> 10:47.800
here

10:48.240 --> 10:49.000
right?

11:00.360 --> 11:01.120
Okay,

11:01.480 --> 11:02.440
let's continue.

11:03.040 --> 11:03.760
Xia,

11:04.480 --> 11:05.400
say something.

11:18.680 --> 11:19.640
Honey!

11:20.120 --> 11:21.680
Guess you're still in that meeting.

11:22.120 --> 11:24.640
Message me back when you're done okay?

11:25.000 --> 11:25.880
Miss you.

11:57.080 --> 11:57.880
This is good.

12:02.440 --> 12:03.760
Waitress. Clean it up.

12:17.360 --> 12:18.760
What are you doing?

12:20.120 --> 12:21.600
There are a lot of people here.

12:22.000 --> 12:23.880
You're so bad.

12:24.600 --> 12:25.600
Quiet for a second,

12:26.440 --> 12:27.640
she just called me.

12:27.640 --> 12:28.720
I didn't even answer.

12:29.000 --> 12:30.440
Let me call her back.

12:31.480 --> 12:32.720
What are you doing, sweetheart?

12:33.000 --> 12:34.240
Answer the phone.

12:34.880 --> 12:36.040
What are you doing, sweetheart?

12:40.760 --> 12:41.720
Xiong Dun!

12:44.640 --> 12:45.400
Xiong Dun!

12:47.360 --> 12:48.160
Xiong Dun!

12:49.000 --> 12:49.800
Xiong Dun!

14:27.400 --> 14:28.280
<i>Xiong,</i>

14:28.280 --> 14:29.320
<i>Happy birthday!</i>

14:29.680 --> 14:30.600
<i>As expected,</i>

14:30.600 --> 14:31.680
<i>I gotta work overtime.</i>

14:31.680 --> 14:32.840
<i>Sorry I can't come.</i>

14:32.840 --> 14:33.800
<i>We'll celebrate another day.</i>

14:33.800 --> 14:34.600
<i>Xiong,</i>

14:34.600 --> 14:36.400
<i>Stupid manager is dragging
everyone to dinner,</i>

14:36.400 --> 14:37.480
<i>you're lucky you got away,</i>

14:37.480 --> 14:38.200
<i>Gotta go.</i>

14:38.200 --> 14:38.920
<i>We'll talk tomorrow</i>

14:39.400 --> 14:40.600
<i>Xiong, I've got a game tomorrow,</i>

14:40.600 --> 14:41.560
<i>you guys have fun.</i>

14:41.560 --> 14:42.760
<i>I'll head over after the match.</i>

14:52.080 --> 14:54.520
[Your mom]

14:57.840 --> 14:58.800
Mom.

14:58.800 --> 14:59.680
<i>Sweetheart,</i>

15:00.000 --> 15:02.040
Happy birthday!

15:03.480 --> 15:04.640
Thanks mom.

15:04.920 --> 15:06.520
<i>You guys finished decorating?</i>

15:06.520 --> 15:07.480
Yes, just finished.

15:07.480 --> 15:08.840
We're letting it ventilate a little bit.

15:08.840 --> 15:11.560
<i>Next time you're back,
you could stay at our new house.</i>

15:11.560 --> 15:12.680
ls dad there?

15:12.680 --> 15:13.640
Yeah, he's here.

15:13.640 --> 15:14.720
<i>Papa Xiong,</i>

15:15.560 --> 15:16.800
<i>Come here. Our daughter is on the phone.</i>

15:18.080 --> 15:18.800
Coming.

15:18.800 --> 15:20.680
<i>Your dad is messing with his plants again.</i>

15:20.680 --> 15:21.600
<i>Hurry up.</i>

15:22.200 --> 15:23.040
<i>Hurry,</i>

15:24.000 --> 15:24.880
<i>Dun, honey,</i>

15:24.880 --> 15:26.160
<i>Happy birthday!</i>

15:26.160 --> 15:27.240
I asked around,

15:27.480 --> 15:29.600
there are plenty of good jobs for you here.

15:29.600 --> 15:30.760
You should come back.

15:30.760 --> 15:31.920
It's better here.

15:31.920 --> 15:33.080
The air is fresh.

15:33.080 --> 15:34.640
It's her birthday today.

15:34.640 --> 15:36.000
Stop with your blabbering.

15:36.000 --> 15:36.760
<i>Your dad,</i>

15:36.760 --> 15:38.160
<i>he's always so chatty.</i>

15:38.160 --> 15:39.800
<i>How are you celebrating today?</i>

15:41.720 --> 15:42.640
I'll be with...

15:43.400 --> 15:44.480
Lao Zheng,

15:44.480 --> 15:45.640
<i>Xiao Xia,</i>

15:46.120 --> 15:47.680
<i>and Emmy.</i>

15:48.480 --> 15:50.240
They bought a huge cake for me.

15:50.480 --> 15:52.200
<i>Don't eat too much cake.</i>

15:52.200 --> 15:54.280
Sugar is not good for you.

15:55.160 --> 15:56.600
I know, I know.

15:56.600 --> 15:57.840
We're gonna go now.

15:57.840 --> 15:59.080
Talk soon.

15:59.080 --> 15:59.840
<i>Bye.</i>

16:00.280 --> 16:00.920
Okay, okay, okay.

16:20.440 --> 16:23.400
[See you there]

16:26.240 --> 16:28.480
Surprise!

16:30.000 --> 16:33.760
May your fortune rise as high as the sky!

16:33.760 --> 16:37.080
We wish you a happy birthday!

16:37.080 --> 16:38.640
Come on. Picture time!

16:40.040 --> 16:41.760
You guys suck.

16:42.480 --> 16:43.760
If you guys showed up a little later,

16:43.760 --> 16:45.440
I probably would've killed myself.

16:45.680 --> 16:47.560
It's just a job.

16:47.560 --> 16:49.080
Coward.

16:49.400 --> 16:50.880
I didn't see you stand up for me today.

16:52.840 --> 16:53.640
Well...

16:53.640 --> 16:54.600
Let this one go,

16:54.600 --> 16:57.080
He did a good job preparing your party.

16:57.080 --> 16:58.120
Very dependable.

16:58.480 --> 16:59.360
Here.

16:59.360 --> 17:00.120
Take these.

17:02.720 --> 17:05.000
How's this gift for you?

17:10.240 --> 17:12.000
How did you guys find out?

17:13.319 --> 17:15.880
The jerk was showing off on his profile.

17:15.880 --> 17:16.920
What?

17:16.920 --> 17:18.440
Said something like,
his dreams are finally coming true.

17:18.440 --> 17:19.520
What an ass.

17:19.520 --> 17:21.440
We never liked that jerk actually.

17:21.720 --> 17:23.319
Really don't know what you see in him.

17:23.319 --> 17:24.720
Now you tell me...

17:28.440 --> 17:29.360
Emmy,

17:29.360 --> 17:32.040
how about the jerk you're dating,
let's make him a target too.

17:32.760 --> 17:33.840
That's right, Emmy.

17:33.840 --> 17:35.280
How could I forget you?

17:35.280 --> 17:36.440
If we put all the boyfriends together
and had a competition,

17:36.440 --> 17:38.160
You'd win, for sure.

17:38.480 --> 17:39.600
Let me tell you,

17:39.600 --> 17:40.920
if it were up to me,

17:40.920 --> 17:41.800
I'd pretend to be single.

17:41.800 --> 17:43.480
When she found out about it,

17:43.480 --> 17:44.640
he'd say stuff like he's got marriage problems.

17:44.640 --> 17:46.400
I'd slap the crap out of him.

17:46.760 --> 17:47.480
Alright, okay,

17:47.480 --> 17:48.480
everybody,

17:48.480 --> 17:49.480
today is a day for celebration.

17:49.480 --> 17:51.520
We should talk about something more cheerful.

17:52.200 --> 17:52.880
Xiong,

17:53.160 --> 17:54.000
for you.

17:55.000 --> 17:55.800
Oh.

17:55.800 --> 17:56.840
Hey, listen,

17:56.840 --> 17:58.240
I wrote this song.

17:58.480 --> 17:59.360
Love it.

18:02.440 --> 18:04.360
You should quit your stupid job, like I did.

18:04.360 --> 18:06.640
Let's start fresh, together.

18:07.120 --> 18:07.920
Xiong,

18:07.920 --> 18:09.120
I don't think that was quitting.

18:09.400 --> 18:10.400
You were fired!

18:11.480 --> 18:13.000
- Say it again, I dare you!
-Stop, stop.

18:13.000 --> 18:13.800
Else,

18:13.800 --> 18:15.120
you can kiss your present goodbye.

18:16.000 --> 18:17.440
That's more like it.

18:19.000 --> 18:20.160
Why is it so light?

18:20.160 --> 18:21.360
Did you write me a check?

18:27.240 --> 18:28.120
Holy...

18:28.120 --> 18:29.000
Xiao Xia,

18:29.240 --> 18:30.600
thanks a lot.

18:30.600 --> 18:31.920
Man, you are generous.

18:31.920 --> 18:32.920
Let me tell you,

18:32.920 --> 18:35.000
I've been saving those numbers for a long time.

18:35.240 --> 18:37.200
You know how much the jackpot is now?

18:37.480 --> 18:39.280
Over 200 million!

18:39.280 --> 18:41.400
This would have worked usually,

18:41.400 --> 18:43.480
but today is the worst day of my life.

18:43.480 --> 18:44.320
Silly girl.

18:44.320 --> 18:46.520
All this means your luck's
about to turn around.

18:46.520 --> 18:47.480
I think so too.

18:47.480 --> 18:48.720
I really hope my bad luck ends right now.

18:50.360 --> 18:51.200
When life sucks,

18:51.200 --> 18:52.120
most of the time,

18:52.120 --> 18:53.120
you could only share

18:53.120 --> 18:54.560
so little.

18:54.920 --> 18:56.360
As for the rest,

18:57.520 --> 18:58.800
just tell them to go away.

18:58.800 --> 18:59.440
That's right!

18:59.440 --> 19:00.560
Let them all just go away!

19:00.560 --> 19:01.480
Cheers!

19:14.360 --> 19:15.720
Go away!

19:15.720 --> 19:16.880
Bosses!

19:16.880 --> 19:18.080
Go away!

19:18.080 --> 19:19.560
Jerks!

19:19.560 --> 19:20.840
Go away!

19:20.840 --> 19:21.840
Overtime!

19:22.360 --> 19:23.680
Go away!

19:23.680 --> 19:24.800
Smog!

19:25.080 --> 19:26.720
Go away!

19:28.480 --> 19:29.560
Landlord...

19:45.520 --> 19:48.160
You don't have to start over
after every breakup.

19:48.400 --> 19:49.600
Save it for the next guy.

