42:29.720 --> 42:31.760
Dying is just sleeping for a long, long time.

42:31.760 --> 42:33.480
It's what my grandma told me.

42:34.240 --> 42:36.080
Then, are you afraid of sleeping
for a really, really long lime?

42:36.760 --> 42:39.040
I like sleeping, it's comfortable.

42:39.040 --> 42:41.040
