42:52.040 --> 42:54.240
I promise I will never bully with you again.

42:56.840 --> 42:57.720
Sure.

42:59.520 --> 43:01.320
Storytime!

43:03.480 --> 43:06.200
Let's see... what story should I tell?

43:07.920 --> 43:09.160
A long,

43:09.160 --> 43:10.720
long time ago,

43:11.200 --> 43:13.880
there was a little boy who knew magic.

43:13.880 --> 43:15.040
His name was Mao Dou.

43:15.040 --> 43:17.160
Hey, he has the same name as me.

43:17.160 --> 43:18.000
Yep, that's right.

43:20.200 --> 43:21.520
One day,

43:21.760 --> 43:22.480
Mao Dou

43:22.480 --> 43:25.800
had awoken from a beautiful, sweet dream,

43:26.360 --> 43:28.720
and realized the world around
him was perfectly tranquil.

43:29.280 --> 43:30.080
The sky,

43:30.080 --> 43:31.600
was unbelievably blue.

43:32.280 --> 43:33.200
Mao Dou

43:33.200 --> 43:34.880
was wearing the coolest,

43:34.880 --> 43:36.560
newest clothing.

43:36.800 --> 43:38.000
He ran through the streets,

43:38.000 --> 43:39.160
he ran,

43:39.400 --> 43:40.520
jumped,

43:42.080 --> 43:43.400
and ran,

43:43.720 --> 43:46.240
until he came to a garden.

43:47.040 --> 43:48.480
Inside that garden,

43:48.480 --> 43:51.480
there were beautiful,
colorful flowers everywhere.

43:51.480 --> 43:52.680
There were few different kinds...

44:07.480 --> 44:08.480
A monster appeared,

44:08.480 --> 44:09.560
Mao Dou struck back.

44:13.440 --> 44:14.200
Do you like it?

44:14.920 --> 44:15.800
Here, for you.

44:18.480 --> 44:20.000
This is awesome. Thank you Xiong!

44:21.760 --> 44:23.640
Let me tell you a secret.

44:23.640 --> 44:26.760
Dr. Liang's girlfriend died from a disease!

44:28.640 --> 44:29.280
It's true.

44:29.280 --> 44:30.680
I heard it from the head nurse.

44:30.680 --> 44:31.720
She's so scary,

44:31.720 --> 44:33.080
I don't think she tells lies.

44:33.640 --> 44:35.680
I can only help you so much,

44:35.680 --> 44:38.000
the rest is up to you.

44:47.800 --> 44:48.840
Mao Dou.

44:48.840 --> 44:49.760
Let's go home.

44:52.120 --> 44:52.920
Let's go.

44:52.920 --> 44:53.680
Time to go home!

44:56.000 --> 44:57.200
Bye-bye!
Bye-bye!

44:59.080 --> 45:00.000
Let's go.

45:04.880 --> 45:07.000
<i>Sometimes, living in your own imagination</i>

45:07.600 --> 45:09.560
<i>is a rather wonderful thing.</i>

45:10.440 --> 45:12.400
<i>You wouldn't have a worry in the world.</i>

45:12.840 --> 45:14.080
<i>No fears.</i>

45:14.360 --> 45:15.480
<i>No grief.</i>

45:16.120 --> 45:17.600
<i>Not even death.</i>

45:28.720 --> 45:30.000
It's you.

45:30.000 --> 45:31.240
Why are you out so late?

45:33.200 --> 45:34.480
I couldn't sleep.

45:34.480 --> 45:36.120
I came out for some moon-bathing.

45:36.800 --> 45:37.800
No way...

45:38.360 --> 45:39.760
The nurse tells me that

45:39.760 --> 45:41.200
out of all the patients,

45:41.200 --> 45:42.360
you are the one who eats the most,

45:42.360 --> 45:43.040
and sleeps the best.

45:44.520 --> 45:46.160
Who told you that?

45:46.160 --> 45:47.600
Bad mouthing me on purpose.

45:48.080 --> 45:50.080
She's obviously jealous of my stunning looks.

45:55.480 --> 45:57.640
Do I have the same disease as Mao Dou?

46:03.520 --> 46:04.600
Patients

46:04.600 --> 46:05.720
must avoid

46:06.040 --> 46:07.560
thinking too much.

46:08.480 --> 46:09.480
It's like this.

46:09.880 --> 46:11.120
It's my responsibility to treat you,

46:11.480 --> 46:12.800
and it's your responsibility to believe in me.

46:13.320 --> 46:14.640
Let's wait for the results to come in.

46:15.320 --> 46:17.240
So, I'm really gonna believe you now.

46:17.640 --> 46:18.880
My life

46:18.880 --> 46:20.120
is in your hands now.

46:20.640 --> 46:21.680
Pinkie swear.

46:23.480 --> 46:24.560
You don't know pinkie swear?

46:24.560 --> 46:26.040
Even a 3 years old would know.

46:26.440 --> 46:27.560
Here, like this,

46:27.560 --> 46:28.480
then, stamp.

46:30.880 --> 46:32.200
This way, if you don't keep your promise,

46:32.720 --> 46:33.840
I will curse you

46:34.160 --> 46:35.520
to remain single for the rest of your life.

46:36.000 --> 46:37.440
That's harsh.

46:40.600 --> 46:42.080
How long have you been a doctor?

46:43.120 --> 46:44.240
Seven years now.

46:45.680 --> 46:46.360
What about you?

46:46.360 --> 46:47.840
What do you do?

46:48.760 --> 46:49.560
Right now,

46:49.560 --> 46:51.280
I draw to make a living.

46:51.720 --> 46:52.840
Artist...

46:53.480 --> 46:54.640
That's good.

46:54.880 --> 46:56.320
Better than us.

46:56.800 --> 46:58.520
It's tough being a doctor.

46:58.520 --> 46:59.760
There's always so much risk involved,

46:59.760 --> 47:01.240
but rarely a sense of accomplishment.

47:01.480 --> 47:02.200
That's easy.

47:02.200 --> 47:03.560
Treat me!

47:03.560 --> 47:05.800
I'm the best at making people
feel accomplished.

47:06.440 --> 47:07.920
How can you do it?

47:08.280 --> 47:09.560
I feel like anything

47:09.560 --> 47:11.720
and everything can make you happy.

47:11.720 --> 47:12.800
I'm silly.

47:13.360 --> 47:14.320
When I was in college,

47:14.320 --> 47:15.640
no one took me seriously.

47:16.040 --> 47:17.480
Happy or not,

47:17.480 --> 47:18.840
we still got to live on, one day at a time.

47:18.840 --> 47:20.400
So just live life to its fullest,
without a care in the world.

47:21.400 --> 47:22.160
Yeah.

47:22.560 --> 47:23.520
That makes sense.

47:24.200 --> 47:25.880
If it makes sense,
then why are you still so serious?

47:28.400 --> 47:29.480
That's right!

47:30.000 --> 47:31.280
You have no idea how important

47:31.280 --> 47:32.480
a doctor's smile can be

47:32.480 --> 47:34.040
for us patients.

47:34.320 --> 47:35.520
So take it from me,

47:35.840 --> 47:38.160
learn to smile and grin
at yourself in the mirror.

47:38.680 --> 47:40.320
Because when you smile,

47:40.320 --> 47:42.080
you're so handsome,
you make me wanna take off...

47:43.640 --> 47:46.200
<i>I really want to slap myself a few limes.</i>

47:48.200 --> 47:50.120
Watch your mouth!

47:52.480 --> 47:53.560
Take off my old identity and be reborn again.

47:54.640 --> 47:55.920
You wanted to say,

47:55.920 --> 47:57.000
take off your clothes?

48:06.480 --> 48:07.360
Hello?

48:07.880 --> 48:08.520
OK.

48:08.520 --> 48:09.720
OK. I'll be right there.

48:11.480 --> 48:13.240
It's been fun talking to you.

48:13.240 --> 48:14.240
I gotta go work.

48:14.240 --> 48:15.160
Get some sleep.

48:40.720 --> 48:43.440
You guys should contact
Xiong Dun's parents soon.

48:43.840 --> 48:45.560
It's better if they are here.

48:45.560 --> 48:47.080
What does she have?

48:47.440 --> 48:48.360
Her condition

48:48.800 --> 48:50.000
is very complicated.

48:51.080 --> 48:53.000
So it's best if her parents are here,

48:53.320 --> 48:54.240
so we could talk about it together.

48:54.240 --> 48:54.920
Ok?

48:55.200 --> 48:57.080
Please tell us how she's doing,

48:57.080 --> 48:58.640
so we'll have an idea of what to prepare for.

48:58.640 --> 49:00.360
I know you care about her a lot.

49:00.360 --> 49:01.080
Dr. Liang please don't move.

49:01.080 --> 49:02.080
Don't move at all.

49:02.080 --> 49:03.520
Here is the thing,
this is for your own good.

49:03.520 --> 49:05.000
She was once the biggest badass
of our neighborhood.

49:05.000 --> 49:06.440
They used to call her Miss Tyson.

49:13.480 --> 49:15.800
[Diagnosis: Non-Hodgkin Lymphoma)

49:26.640 --> 49:27.800
I don't think

49:27.800 --> 49:29.040
we should tell her

49:29.040 --> 49:30.400
unless it's absolutely necessary.

49:31.120 --> 49:32.600
What if she couldn't handle it,

49:32.600 --> 49:33.520
and just... gives up hope altogether.

49:34.120 --> 49:34.840
Xiao Xia,

49:35.520 --> 49:37.080
if you were the one who's sick,

49:37.080 --> 49:38.280
would you rather find out now,

49:38.280 --> 49:39.200
or later,

49:39.200 --> 49:40.360
or be kept in the dark the whole time?

49:41.760 --> 49:43.600
If it was me,

49:44.840 --> 49:46.160
I would rather know it

49:46.160 --> 49:47.240
sooner...

49:47.240 --> 49:47.840
Never mind.

49:47.840 --> 49:48.840
I don't think you should ask me anymore.

49:48.840 --> 49:49.480
Okay, that's enough.

49:49.480 --> 49:50.560
You can never decide on anything,

49:50.560 --> 49:51.520
it's useless asking you.

49:51.520 --> 49:53.280
How about we vote on it?

49:53.280 --> 49:54.600
Raise your hand if you agree to tell her now.

49:57.520 --> 49:59.320
Xiao Xia, are you going to
raise your hand or not?

50:08.280 --> 50:09.440
Why are you here?

50:09.440 --> 50:11.720
I am starving.

50:12.680 --> 50:13.760
Excuse me.

50:14.600 --> 50:16.280
Hello. Can I help you?

50:16.280 --> 50:17.680
This one.

50:18.200 --> 50:18.920
This too.

50:19.320 --> 50:20.280
Quickly.

50:20.280 --> 50:21.360
OK. It'll be right out.

50:21.360 --> 50:22.160
Thanks.

50:22.600 --> 50:23.400
Are you crazy?

50:23.400 --> 50:24.160
Can you eat all that?

50:25.000 --> 50:27.520
I mean you only live once right,

50:27.520 --> 50:28.480
one meal eaten

50:28.480 --> 50:29.560
is one meal less.

50:40.200 --> 50:41.160
I want to

50:41.160 --> 50:42.920
tell you guys something.

50:44.000 --> 50:44.800
I really

50:45.280 --> 50:46.120
hit the jackpot this time.

50:46.440 --> 50:47.240
200 million?

50:47.480 --> 50:49.520
Dude, where is the context?
Pay attention please.

50:51.840 --> 50:52.800
So you know?

50:54.320 --> 50:56.440
It was cleverness that
killed the cat, not curiosity.

50:59.720 --> 51:00.400
Xiong,

51:00.640 --> 51:02.440
we've asked around.

51:02.440 --> 51:03.440
It's not that big of a deal.

51:03.840 --> 51:05.360
On a tumor scale,

51:05.360 --> 51:06.760
this only ranks number 10 on the chart.

51:07.800 --> 51:08.680
Tumor?

51:09.360 --> 51:10.360
What tumor?

51:12.240 --> 51:13.520
I thought you already knew?

51:14.120 --> 51:15.440
I have a tumor?

51:16.520 --> 51:17.680
It's not leukemia?

51:19.760 --> 51:20.800
Oh thank god!

51:21.200 --> 51:22.640
I thought I had leukemia!

51:22.640 --> 51:23.440
Really.

51:23.760 --> 51:24.840
Thank God!

51:24.840 --> 51:25.840
And Buddha!

51:30.160 --> 51:31.320
Why do you look so worried?

51:32.280 --> 51:33.560
It's a tumor...

51:33.560 --> 51:34.640
Just cut it off!

51:39.000 --> 51:40.120
From now on,

51:40.400 --> 51:41.440
I'm gonna be healthy!

51:41.440 --> 51:42.640
No more laziness.

51:42.640 --> 51:43.840
No more junk food.

51:43.840 --> 51:44.760
When I'm all better,

51:44.760 --> 51:45.560
I'm going to workout everyday,

51:45.560 --> 51:46.400
for two hours.

51:47.080 --> 51:47.800
No, for three hours!

51:48.400 --> 51:49.320
I am still in the middle of getting
an IV injection,

51:49.320 --> 51:50.840
you guys eat this junk food.

52:00.720 --> 52:02.360
You totally know her.

52:03.080 --> 52:04.280
Look at her.

52:04.560 --> 52:05.360
"It's a tumor."

52:05.360 --> 52:06.640
"Just cut it off."

52:07.200 --> 52:07.880
Come on dude!

52:07.880 --> 52:10.120
Have you forgotten all your bio classes?

52:11.160 --> 52:12.400
It's lymphoma.

52:12.640 --> 52:14.200
Lymph nodes are all over the body.

52:15.040 --> 52:15.920
Cut it off?

52:15.920 --> 52:17.440
How about I cut you off!

52:29.520 --> 52:30.720
What are you looking for?

52:31.040 --> 52:32.400
Xiong Dun wants to watch "The Walking Dead'.

52:32.400 --> 52:33.560
I made a DVD for her last time.

52:33.560 --> 52:34.680
Why can't I find it?

52:34.680 --> 52:36.120
And her comic books too.

52:37.120 --> 52:38.320
Come get something to eat first.

52:38.320 --> 52:39.640
You didn't eat much for lunch.

52:40.080 --> 52:40.800
Emmy,

52:40.800 --> 52:42.120
you too, come eat something.

52:42.120 --> 52:43.120
I'm not hungry.

52:47.560 --> 52:48.680
What's the matter?

52:49.000 --> 52:50.040
Are you ok?

52:50.680 --> 52:52.360
How can I be ok?

52:54.120 --> 52:56.400
My best friend is lying in the hospital.

52:59.800 --> 53:00.840
Lao Zheng,

53:01.320 --> 53:02.280
don't...

53:03.480 --> 53:04.440
Shut Up!

53:07.320 --> 53:08.480
Eat your noodles.

53:19.280 --> 53:21.640
Can you be any louder eating
those damn noodles!

53:52.240 --> 53:54.520
[Go away Mr. Tumor]

54:10.640 --> 54:12.080
What do you mean?

54:12.880 --> 54:14.240
You've already done it!

54:14.240 --> 54:15.320
Why are you calling me now

54:15.320 --> 54:17.280
and pretend to be a good guy?

54:17.280 --> 54:18.920
You jerk!

54:19.720 --> 54:21.440
Answer the phone!

54:42.480 --> 54:43.760
<i>Her name, is Xia Meng.</i>

54:44.240 --> 54:46.640
<i>She was kicked out of her old room,</i>

54:46.640 --> 54:48.120
<i>and has become my bed mate.</i>

54:49.000 --> 54:49.920
<i>Whenever the sound of</i>

54:49.920 --> 54:51.760
<i>a retro Vespa is heard,</i>

54:51.760 --> 54:52.920
<i>she would show up</i>

54:52.920 --> 54:54.200
<i>a few minutes later.</i>

54:55.080 --> 54:56.240
<i>She rarely smiles.</i>

54:56.480 --> 54:57.480
<i>When she's not on the phone,</i>

54:57.480 --> 54:58.560
<i>she barely speaks.</i>

54:58.880 --> 54:59.600
<i>And when she's on the phone,</i>

54:59.600 --> 55:00.880
<i>the cursing almost never ends.</i>

55:01.880 --> 55:04.240
<i>She would always receive
flowers and fruit baskets,</i>

55:04.680 --> 55:06.160
<i>but no one has ever visited.</i>

55:06.880 --> 55:07.720
<i>So the flowers,</i>

55:07.720 --> 55:08.800
<i>goes in the trash.</i>

55:09.280 --> 55:10.200
<i>And the fruits,</i>

55:10.200 --> 55:11.600
<i>are left there to rot.</i>

55:23.320 --> 55:24.120
Go ahead.

55:30.720 --> 55:32.240
<i>I don't know why.</i>

55:32.240 --> 55:33.880
<i>But it doesn't matter what Meng says,</i>

55:33.880 --> 55:36.120
<i>I always feel an impulse to say, "yes ma'am."</i>

55:55.520 --> 55:56.600
What is it?

55:57.480 --> 55:59.120
I have bestowed these upon thee,

56:00.200 --> 56:01.800
how dare you not accept.

56:07.080 --> 56:09.080
Thank you, thank you for
your kindness, your highness.

56:38.480 --> 56:39.320
<i>Doctor,</i>

56:39.320 --> 56:40.360
<i>Can you please tell me,</i>

56:40.360 --> 56:41.320
<i>You see,</i>

56:41.320 --> 56:42.640
<i>I'm looking for...</i>

56:43.000 --> 56:44.440
<i>Uh oh...</i>

56:45.440 --> 56:47.120
<i>I knew this day would come.</i>

56:47.480 --> 56:49.480
<i>But I didn't expect it to come so soon.</i>

56:52.400 --> 56:53.520
[Unknown call]

56:54.800 --> 56:55.320
Hello?

56:55.320 --> 56:56.360
Hi Mr. Xiong,

56:56.360 --> 56:57.720
I'm your daughter's friend.

56:57.720 --> 56:58.720
She is sick.

56:58.720 --> 57:00.000
She's in the hosp...

57:00.360 --> 57:01.440
Liar.

57:02.720 --> 57:03.560
Bamboo eight.

57:04.080 --> 57:04.800
Hello?

57:04.800 --> 57:06.400
Mr, Xiong, please don't hang up.

57:06.400 --> 57:08.000
Xiong Dun shaved her head when she was six.

57:08.000 --> 57:09.000
When she was seven,
she tried to shave like you,

57:09.000 --> 57:10.000
and cut her lips.

57:10.000 --> 57:10.720
And one summer,

57:10.720 --> 57:12.640
your brought her to a farm to watch
an irrigation plane,

57:12.640 --> 57:13.720
but almost lost her.

57:13.720 --> 57:15.120
And also, before she turned 16,

57:15.120 --> 57:17.160
she weight the heaviest at 180 pounds.

57:17.160 --> 57:17.920
Who is this?

57:18.400 --> 57:19.600
Let my daughter go!

57:26.600 --> 57:27.600
This is

57:28.000 --> 57:29.400
a systemic disease.

57:30.240 --> 57:31.840
It's very hard to treat.

57:32.280 --> 57:33.040
Within 5 years,

57:33.040 --> 57:34.000
the survival rate

57:34.000 --> 57:35.560
is no more than 20 percent.

57:36.720 --> 57:38.640
What we can do now is

57:38.640 --> 57:40.400
sessions of systematic chemotherapy

57:41.040 --> 57:42.800
to prolong life.

57:43.760 --> 57:46.040
However,

57:46.040 --> 57:46.760
migraines,

57:46.760 --> 57:47.840
hair loss.

57:48.800 --> 57:50.560
These are side effects of the chemo.

57:50.560 --> 57:51.240
So,

57:51.240 --> 57:52.400
don't be too nervous.

57:54.040 --> 57:56.760
Our goal for late stage cancer patients is

57:57.440 --> 57:59.200
to improve their quality of life

57:59.880 --> 58:01.680
and prolong the time they have left.

58:32.320 --> 58:33.920
Go be with her.

58:34.240 --> 58:35.280
I'm going...

58:35.640 --> 58:36.880
buy some stuff.

59:51.000 --> 59:52.440
It's not a big problem.
You'll get better.

59:52.440 --> 59:53.640
You are always too rebellious

59:53.640 --> 59:54.760
Do you remember?

59:54.760 --> 59:56.920
What I tell you every time I call you.

59:56.920 --> 59:58.520
You have to eat well,

59:58.800 --> 01:00:01.000
and wrap yourself up when it's cold.

01:00:01.000 --> 01:00:02.440
You always wear so little.

01:00:02.800 --> 01:00:03.640
You never listen...

01:00:04.840 --> 01:00:06.000
You always sleep so late,

01:00:06.000 --> 01:00:06.880
and wake up even later.

01:00:07.200 --> 01:00:08.240
You'd draw for hours and hours,

01:00:08.240 --> 01:00:09.720
without eating or drinking.
Nobody could take that.

01:00:11.400 --> 01:00:13.040
What happened to your mouth?

01:00:18.160 --> 01:00:19.080
Give it to me!

01:00:22.400 --> 01:00:23.280
Give it to me!

01:00:25.160 --> 01:00:26.160
How many times have I told you?

01:00:26.160 --> 01:00:27.560
Your father's side has a history of diabetes,

01:00:27.560 --> 01:00:28.520
you can't eat too many sweets.

01:00:28.520 --> 01:00:29.320
Maybe you got sick from

01:00:29.320 --> 01:00:30.800
all this carelessness.

01:00:31.680 --> 01:00:33.240
Please stop nagging me.

01:00:33.240 --> 01:00:34.640
I'm already like this.

01:00:34.640 --> 01:00:36.240
It's only a piece of chocolate.

01:00:36.240 --> 01:00:37.000
I'm sorry.

01:00:37.000 --> 01:00:38.480
I won't eat it again.

01:00:38.760 --> 01:00:40.240
You have to change.

01:00:40.240 --> 01:00:41.040
Listen to me,

01:00:41.040 --> 01:00:41.720
to get well,

01:00:41.720 --> 01:00:42.880
you should come back home.

01:00:42.880 --> 01:00:44.400
Stop messing around in this city.

01:00:45.520 --> 01:00:46.560
I'm not going back.

01:00:46.560 --> 01:00:48.160
I've just started my career here.

01:00:48.160 --> 01:00:49.680
What career?

01:00:49.680 --> 01:00:50.440
It's been how many years
since you've graduated?

01:00:50.440 --> 01:00:51.680
You're still living like this.

01:00:52.440 --> 01:00:53.120
If you don't go back,

01:00:53.120 --> 01:00:54.280
your dad and I will sell the new apartment

01:00:54.280 --> 01:00:56.120
and move here to live with you.

01:00:56.120 --> 01:00:57.480
That would drive me crazy, mom.

01:00:57.480 --> 01:00:59.280
You taking care of yourself drives us crazy.

01:01:07.120 --> 01:01:08.000
